title: Slow Love
description: A lonely snail lookin' for love literally crashes into the treehouse and asks Finn and Jake for help. Now, our heroes must teach this snail how to get a girlfriend before he destroys their home!

title: Knock It Off
description: When the Professor's college roommate sees his old pal's brilliant creations, he decides to cash in on the popularity of the Powerpuffs.

title: Banana Joe
description: Cuando el director Brown le asigna a Darwin la tarea de hacer el anuario escolar, Darwin comienza pidiéndole a Banana Joe, el payaso de la clase, una simple selfi para la portada. Pero con Banana Joe, las cosas nunca son tan simples.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: The New Crystal Gems
description: Connie helps look after Beach City while Steven is busy.

title: Know It All
description: When Vic accidently unleashes evil bats from a cave, it's up to the boys and Don to protect the town, but Vic's know-it-all attitude keeps getting in the way.

title: My Fair Carol
description: KO, Enid and Rad team up to help Carol out with a special occasion.

title: The Island
description: While trying to sail to Japan, the Baby Bears get stranded on an island. Luckily, they meet Dave and Karla, who help with survival on the island while looking for an escape.

title: Hoyo En 10
description: Mientras Ben juega al minigolf, lo atacan los Ground Hawgs, una pandilla de mutantes convertidos en ciclistas del Doctor Ánimo. Pero cuando los Hawgs se dan cuenta de que la falsa aldea de minigolf no es un lugar real, Ben debe transformarse en alienígena para detenerlos antes de que elijan la ciudad verdadera que está a pocos metros de allí como su blanco.

title: It Grows
description: As everyone celebrates Valentino for growing his first facial hair, a jealous Vic resorts to magical methods to grow a mustache and compete for attention.

title: The Fatal Fare
description: Space Cabbie inadvertently learns about a great threat to the Justice League when one of his passengers turns out to be Darkseid.

title: Fistfull of Balloons
description: When Vic gets double-crossed during a water balloon fight, he goes on a revenge mission to find out who was responsible.

title: Jeff Wins
description: Jeff enlists Clarence to help him prepare for the big Aberdale cook-off. Will Jeff keep his cool or freak out and toss his dish away like in years past?

title: Earthlings
description: Amethyst tries to exact revenge with a showdown in the Kindergarten.

title: Robo Teacher
description: When a substitute teacher fills in for Chef, Duncan thinks it's going to be the best day ever. He's wrong.

title: Mumm-Ra of Plun-Darr Part 2
description: Chaos reigns over Third Earth now that the Mutants and Mumm-Ra control the Cats' Lair! The Thundercats' only hope is to sneak back in and get a super secret weapon Panthro has hidden at the heart of the Lair.

title: While You Were Away
description: Dr. Psychobos and Princess Attea have invaded Rook's home planet Revonnah with an army of Incurseans! (Introducing new Ben alien, Astrodactyl.)

title: Two Parter Part 1
description: The Titans visit the Hall of Justice to use the pool, but then decide to check out the inside.

title: Two Parter Part 2
description: The Titans must save the members of the Justice League from the clutches of the supervillain Darkseid.

title: Let's Fight to the End
description: When a fighting tournament is announced at the Plaza, there is more at stake than meets the eye.

title: A Small Problem
description: When Ben is not allowed on an attraction at a water park because he to short, he decides to go alien to get even with the ride's attendant.

title: La princesa de jade
description: A raíz de un cruel ataque al Palacio, Los Hijos de Garmadon roban la segunda Máscara Oni, y los ninjas invitan a la Princesa Real, Harumi, a su improvisada familia.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: The Cube Root
description: When a mysterious alien abducts Mr. Terrific, Batman, Luthor and two of the brainiest villains in the universe, he puts them to a test to discover who is the smartest among them.

title: Fragments
description: Steven heads to the woods to train with a powerful mentor.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Detention
description: After Clarence discovers that Mr. Reese falls asleep during detention when given a doughnut, it becomes the spot to be during recess. When Jeff gets wind of it he transforms it from a fun hang out spot to a too-cool-for-school club.

title: Battle for Cybertron I Part 1
description: As the Autobots on the Ark prepare to land on Cybertron, Chromia and Perceptor attempt to escape Decepticon captivity.

title: El chillido de hombre muerto
description: La casi desaparición de Zane a manos del Señor "E" obliga a los ninjas a huir a bordo del Bounty, donde descubren que una tramisión que Zane interceptó puede revelar la ubicación oculta del "Silencioso".
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Crece
description: Mientras todo el mundo celebra a Valentino porque le creció su primer vello facial, Vic se pone celoso y recurre a métodos mágicos para dejarse crecer el bigote y competir por la atención.

title: Breakup
description:
Feeling left out, Adorabat wishes Mao Mao and Badgerclops would spend less time with each other and more time with her. When she gets
what she wishes for and accidentally breaks up their friendship, only the secret of their past can bring them back together.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Avistamiento de Ballenas
description: Manzana y Cebollín necesitan unirse a un club exclusivo para ver una ballena fuera de lo común.

title: Wild Wild Wheel Part 1
description: A dangerous lone gunslinger named WildWheel returns to Cybertron looking for Optimus Prime.

title: Una leccion para todos
description: Los Fantásticos le enseñan a unos chicos del vecindario a no imitar a los demás. Por ejemplo, a quienes utilizan a sus Bakugan con fines frívolos.

title: The Ground Is Lava!
description: When an intense game of "The Ground is Lava" breaks out, Craig must carefully traverse the Creek to save his sister.

title: Ninja Contra Lava
description: Los ninja se encuentran atrapados en una pirámide y deben escapar de la lava invasora para advertir a la ciudad de NINJAGO de una nueva invasión serpentina.

title: Hole in 10
description: While mini-golfing, Ben is attacked by the Ground Hawgs, a gang of Dr. Animo mutants turned bikers. When the Hawgs realize the faux mini-golf village isn't an actual town, Ben must go alien to stop them before they set their sights on the real city down the road.

title: Meet Cheetara
description: Cheetara is the coolest cat around! Not only is she so fast that she can outrun lightning, but so clever she can outsmart Mumm-Ra's evil plans! Villains don't stand a chance against Cheetara…well, unless Mumm-Ra uses his Doom Staff, then she might be in trouble.

title: On the Road Song
description: Check out "On the Road" from the We Bare Bears Movie soundtrack.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: Gyranoide del Futuro
description: Manzana y Cebollín se esfuerzan por subir a la montaña rusa más loca del parque de diversiones.

title: We'll Be there Music Video
description: Check out the Extended version of "We'll be There" featuring Estelle from the We Bare Bears Movie!

title: El Camino
description: iEste episodio transcurre cuando los Osos son cachorritos! Los tres Osos, en su viaje por el desierto, se topan con un depósito gigante. Los Osos tratan de convertir este paraíso repleto de cajas en su hogar.

title: Everything's Fine
description: Steven insists that everything is fine.

title: Enemy of My Enemy
description: When a grudge match between Fire Man and Namagem threatens to level Silicon City, Mega Man must intervene and ultimately choose a side to prevent collateral damage.

title: Historia Antigua
description: Mientras Aspheera busca vengarse del "Engañador Traicionero" que la traicionó, el ninja hace un sorprendente descubrimiento.

title: Back to the Library
description: Uncle Grandpa uses time travel to convince his past self to return a library book on time.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Fideito
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben seguir teniendo la onda suficiente para aparecer en el video musical de su rapero favorito.

title: Burger Run/Monkey See, Monkey Don't
description: Burger Run: When the local Burger Joint is being threatened by a rogue Bakugan, Dan steps up to save the day and the burgers!/Monkey See, Monkey Don't: The AO stop neighborhood kids from copycat behavior (namely, using their Bakugan for frivolous reasons).

title: Monstra-City/Shut the Pup Up
description: Monstra-city: When all the monsters move from Monster Isle to Townsville, it's up to the Girls to keep the peace./Shut the Pup Up: When the Talking Dog witnesses a crime, he moves in with the girls for protection. But the girls soon realize this chatterbox dog is less than the perfect pet.

title: Ben 24hrs
description: When Ben (and Gwen!) attempt to stay up all night for Adrenaland, the only theme park open 24/7, he not only fails to utilize his alien powers to stay awake, but his "sleep-alien-ing" causes disaster after disaster that Gwen must fix before things get way out of hand.

title: Separacion
description: Adorabat siente que es dejada de lado y desea que Mao Mao y Colosal pasen menos tiempo juntos y más tiempo con ella. Pero cuando el deseo de Adorabat se hace realidad y destruye la amistad de Mao Mao y Colosal, solo el secreto de su pasado podrá volver a unirlos.

title: Last Laugh
description: Ben's fear of clowns emerges at an unfortunate time when our heroes stumble upon a wicked circus with a psychic vampire clown named Zomobozo.

title: Dendy's Video Channel
description: Dendy tries to update KO's Video Channel for him, but has trouble finding something to post.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: Recipe for Disaster
description: During Chefapalooza in the Rocky Mountains, three famous chefs and infamous bad-guys, The Tri-Chefta, hunt down Wildvine in hopes of creating their most exotic dish to date.

title: Dead Man's Squall
description: Zane's near demise at the hands of Mr. E forces the ninja to flee aboard the Bounty, where they discover that a transmission Zane intercepted may reveal the hidden location of the Quiet One.

title: Boss For a Day
description: When Chata lets Vic be the boss of the taco stand for the day Vic decides to fire Val, which has disastrous consequences.

title: Goldfish Follies
description: Clarence buys a goldfish, but when the goldfish bag breaks before he can get home, Clarence must keep his new friend out of harms way and get him back into water before it's too late.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Grown Up Stuff
description: Puppycorn doesn't want to grow up. To ease his woes, Unikitty spends the day teaching him all the fun things about being an adult.

title: Escape from Monster Island
description: After Bubbles wins two tickets to see the girls' favorite band Sensitive Thugz, Blossom and Buttercup vie for her plus one. But when the Mayor's plane crashes on Monster Island, the girls must put aside their differences to save the day!

title: DIY Baby Bear Embroidery Hoop
description: This is so mesmerizing. Who else wants to try to make this? Embroidery by the talented Jessica Long and Namaste Hand Embroidery!

title: The Never Gwending Story
description: When Chef loses the last page of the story-time book, Gwen takes over and creates a monster that all the kids start to believe in.

title: Too Much of a Goo'd Thing
description: Beth refuses to believe that the adorable goo creature she's created out of slime is consuming the kids until she and Gwen are the only two left in class.

title: Ice Bear Drawing Challenge
description: Drawing challenge time! We tried drawing Ice Bear in 15 seconds, 1 minute, and 5 minutes.

title: Dangerous Dealings/The Hunter Returns
description: Dangerous Dealings: The Awesome Brawler's have become aware of a growing number of adults with illegal Baku-brawling devices. But where are they all coming from? Shun decides to take things into his own hands and sets up a "sting" operation to try to draw out the person selling the devices./The Hunter Returns: Lightning has been caught and locked up by an overly aggressive dog catcher! And to make things worse, he doesn't have his collar with Baku-balls. At the compound where he's being held, he runs into an old foe.  It's up to these two enemies to team up and escape their captor.

title: Hairence
description: It's time for Clarence's first summer job helping out his mom at Hip Clipz Salon School, but when a rude customer bosses around Mary and her staff, Clarence gives her a haircut she'll never forget.

title: I Am My Monster
description: Everything is not fine.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Thunderhowl Part 1
description: Bumblebee and Chromia travel to Crystal City to recover one of Windblade's psychic shards and encounter a long-lost bot.

title: Un almuerzo inesperado
description: Cuando el Restaurante de Hamburguesas es amenazado por un violento Bakugan, Dan llega para salvar el día...y las hamburguesas.

title: NBTS 2: Chapter Two
description: In order to stop Ultralak, the Titans must find three music stems, but will need help from a local Miner to get the first stem away from the Sheriff.

title: The Ringer
description: Sinestro's ring is suddenly much more powerful than usual, so the Justice League sends a microscopic Atom into his ring to find out what the cause might be.

title: The Robot
description: Gumball discovers that Bobert is planning to take over his identity and replace him!

title: Manzana, Concentrate
description: Manzana ayuda a Cebollín a cumplir su sueño de competir en un programa de pastelería.

title: The Secret
description: Gumball almost loses his mind trying to guess Darwin's secret.

title: Old Lady Bodyguard
description: After being "bought" at a charity auction, Hawkodile is forced to spend the day as Old Lady Edith's personal bodyguard.

title: Snake Jaguar
description: In order to join the Sons of Garmadon, Zane (aka Snake Jaguar) participates in a deadly motorcycle initiation race.

title: DIY Bears Mug Hugging Cookies
description: Make your own We Bare Bears cookies. They can hang off of a mug handle, or you can dunk them in your We Bare Bears mug.

title: Ninja vs. Lava
description: The ninja find themselves trapped in a pyramid and must escape encroaching lava to warn NINJAGO City of a new Serpentine invasion.

title: Guar serpiente
description: Para unirse a Los Hijos de Garmadon, Zane (alias Jaguar Serpiente) participa en una carrera de iniciación mortal de motocicletas.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: The Kid From 3030
description: The kids meet a mysterious kid from the future and try to help him complete his mission.

title: Enemy Mime
description: When the Sheriff's Dept fights a monster that copies their every move, they'll have to find a way to fight without fighting.

title: The Cave of Gelatinous Doom!
description: The Warriors don't have a worthy adventure to use their impressive new skull-and-crossbones-emblazoned Bonehead Magisword until they are sent on a quest to battle a mighty slime beast in the Dungeon of Gelatinous Doom!

title: The Saga of Robopiggeh!
description: A botched rescue attempt damages their robot pal, RoboPiggeh, and Vambre and Prohyas must battle the evil cyborg, Tera-Bite, in Galacton, who is determined to dismantle their broken pal for being obsolete.

title: Ben 24 Horas
description: Cuando Ben (iy Gwen!) intenta quedarse despierto toda la noche para ir a Adrenaland -el único parque temático abierto las 24 horas, los siete días de la semana- no solo es incapaz de utilizar sus poderes alienígenas para lograr su objetivo, sino que además su estado de adormecimiento alienígena provoca un desastre tras otro, y Gwen debe arreglar las cosas antes de que todo se salga de control.

title: Homeworld Bound
description: Steven heads to the Diamonds for advice on how to control his new powers.

title: Bromas pesadas
description: Las constantes bromas pesadas de Wynton colman la paciencia de su Bakugan, Trox, quien decide darle una lección.

title: The Fourth Wall
description: Control Freak informs the Titans that they are on a TV show he created and demands they earn him an award.

title: The Spoon
description: Gumball and Darwin are unwitting accomplices in a gas station robbery.

title: Baby Bears on a Plane
description: The Baby Bears have an adventure in the sky while aboard a plane to Sweden. But when the baby Bears are forced to sit in different sections of the plan, things get a bit haywire for everyone on board.

title: The Best VHS in the World
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to return an overdue VHS to the store so they won't be banned from renting new movies.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Meet Tygra
description: The smartest Thundercat, Tygra. Tygra's mission is to make Lion-O a better leader. He might get around to it too, if he wasn't so busy cleaning up after the other Thundercats.

title: Horn, Sweet Horn
description: Bubbles convinces the Professor to test his new transmogrifying ray on her new friend Donny the Pony in an effort to help him become the unicorn he's always wanted to be. But when it turns Donny into a monster instead, she must stop him before he destroys Townsville!

title: Sneak Peek "Internet Frenzy"
description: In their biggest attempt to become internet famous yet, the Bears put every popular internet thing into one video and cause pandemonium throughout the Bay Area.

title: Battle for Cybertron II Part 2
description: The Autobots distract the Decepticons with an all-out assault on the Threshold of the Well while Bee, Hot Rod, and Cheetor split off for the real mission…

title: Bienvenidos al Inframundo Parte 1
description: Después de que Vic pierde una pelea de lucha libre, V&V viajan al inframundo para buscar el consejo de su tío, un famoso luchador llamado El Toro.

title: Battle for Cybertron II Part 1
description: Megatron's jubilation at destroying the Ark is short-lived as he realizes the ship was a decoy — the Autobots have landed on Cybertron.

title: The Brain Buster
description: A mysterious creature abducts Batman, Mr. Terrific, Luthor and two of the brainiest villains in the universe to put them to the test to discover who is the smartest among them.

title: NBTS 2: Chapter One
description: The elderly Titans decide to take one last trip to the world of Night Begins to Shine only to encounter a new villian ruling the land, Ultralak.

title: Replaced
description: Mordecai and Rigby find out that Benson is going to replace them and have to figure out a way to stop it.

title: No Me Impresiona
description: Cuando un Corazoncito no se siente impresionado con las hazañas del departamento del sheriff, nuestros tres héroes intentan de todo para conquistarlo.

title: Lil Noodle
description: Apple and Onion must remain legit enough to be in their favorite rapper's music video.

title: There Are No Hoppy Endings
description: Chef struggles to maintain his sanity when the kids continue to blame a stuffed rabbit named Hoppy for everything they do wrong.

title: El chico del 3030
description: Los niños conocen a un misterioso niño del futuro y tratan de ayudarlo a completar su misión.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Serpientastrofe
description: El ataque de Serpentine en NINJAGO City se ve desde una perspectiva inesperada, completamente al estilo de un noticiero en vivo entregado por Gayle Gossip y su camarógrafo.

title: A Man Man for All Seasons
description: When a run-in with the Hoover Gang leaves Aki unable to transform into Mega Man, he must don a cheap costume and enlist the unlikeliest of sidekicks, Man Man!

title: Tummy Trouble
description: When the Incursean armada kidnaps the Gourmand Queen, Ben and Rook must get the warring Gormand factions to work together to save her and stop the Incursean invasion.

title: Superado
description: Cuando Rufus y Reg llegan para engañar al pueblo, el sheriff Mao Mao les enseña una lección sobre la justicia.

title: The News Never Sleeps!
description: Lil' Nelson takes a job as a paperboy, which is more difficult than it sounds in a city overrun by scorching Pyro Vipers and an evil Serpentine sorceress.

title: The Last Donnycorn
description: When Donny the Unicorn is hunted by a seemingly unstoppable foe, the Powerpuff Girls have to find a way to save him before it's too late!

title: Kevin 11
description: After a big argument with Max, Ben rebels by going out on his own in the Big Apple and makes friends with Kevin 11, who has plans for the Omnitrix.

title: Nano of the North
description: It's raining in Townville, but this is more than just rain. These drops are actually microscopic robots tearing apart the city, and the girls must find a way to fight them on their own level.

title: Members Only
description: When the girls try to join an all-male superhero organization, they learn that sometimes supermen aren't so super.

title: Belly Bros
description: When a kid is bummed that his favorite shirt won't fit over his big belly, it's up to Uncle Grandpa to show him that t-shirts come and go, but having a big belly is always cool.

title: Pet Shop
description: Pet Shop tells the tale of where the Baby Bears once lived, and after a run-in with a video crew shooting a Sarah McLachlan-type animal adoption video, almost seized an opportunity to find a home separated from each other.

title: Apple's Focus
description: Apple helps Onion achieve his dream of competing on a baking show.

title: Beautopia
description: Susan Strong returns to tell Finn and Jake that her world is in danger!

title: Battle for Cybertron I Part 2
description: Chromia and Perceptor race to warn the Autobots that the Decepticons are waiting for them on Cybertron.

title: #LaDulceJusticia - Primera parte
description: En el episodio estreno de cuatro partes de la serie, seis chicas comunes y corrientes se conocen y descubren que tienen poderes extraordinarios. Deciden unir sus fuerzas para derrotar a algunos de los villanos más siniestros de Metrópolis.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Let's Get Shadowy
description: KO teams up with an unlikely ally to take on an old foe.

title: Chimney
description: While playing in the woods the boys befriend a wild dog, bring it home and name it Chimney. When the boys find themselves trapped in a well, the new pup is their only hope for escape.

title: The Tome of Morrow
description: Noville's Magisword training with Vambre pays off and the Warriors invite him on a mission to an ancient cave in the Barren Faceland to find the rare and sacred book, the Tome of Morrow.

title: Meet Mumm-ra and the Mutants
description: The Thundercats have met their match with the evil, undead Mumm-ra! He and the bumbling Mutants have made it their goal to stop the Thundercats by any means necessary, but of course the Thundercats have other plans!

title: System Error
description: When Batman discovers that he and the rest of the League are robots, he investigates to find out who did this and why?

title: #SweetJustice Part 2
description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

title: La mascara del engano
description: Cuando un sindicato de criminals desconocido amenaza a la Familia Real, los ninjas son llamados de nuevo a la acción y deben proteger a la princesa real y un artefacto legendario que puede tener poderes sobrenaturales.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: El bravucon
description: Los Fantásticos deben lidiar con un bravucón que usa a su Bakugan para intimidar a los chicos del vecindario.

title: The Climb
description: Craig's phone gets stuck in Mt. Sycamore, the tallest tree in the creek!

title: Rad
description: With Plumber agents trapped in Incursean territory, Ben and Rook must employ the services of Rad Dudesman, the roughest, toughest smuggler in the galaxy.  (Introducing Rad Dudesman, return of classic Ben alien, Eye Guy.)

title: DIY Origami Bookmarks
description: Cute-tify your bookshelf with these adorable (and easy to make) We Bare Bears origami bookmarks!

title: Demasiada baba
description: Beth se niega a creer que la adorable criatura de baba que ha creado con limo esté comiéndose a los niños hasta que ella y Gwen son las únicas dos que quedan en la clase.

title: Sophie, the Bakuganist/Midnight Train Battle!
description: Sophie, the Bakuganist: Magnus is on the trail of the illegal Baku-brawling devices and, is looking to cut off the supply at its source. When he witnesses an illegal deal going down, he knows it's up to him to go after the shipment to keep the illegal devices off the street./Midnight Train Battle!: Sophie Judson Warfield, a wealthy activist with the Citizens to Save Bakugan Society, is working to put an end to all Bakugan brawling. Her latest target is the Awesome Brawlers themselves. When Wynton doesn't take Sophie seriously, the encounter quickly turns into an all-out Bakugan brawl.

title: The Road
description:
This episode takes place when the Bears are young cubs! The three bears, on their way through the desert, come upon a giant warehouse. It's like an Amazon fulfillment
center. The Bears try to make this box-filled paradise their home.

title: The Jade Princess
description: In the wake of a vicious attack upon the palace, the Sons of Garmadon steal the second Oni Mask, and the ninja invite the royal princess, Harumi, into their makeshift family.

title: Welcome to the Underworld 1
description: After Victor loses a wrestling match, Victor and Valentino journey to the underworld to seek advice from their uncle, a famous wrestler named El Toro.

title: Save Mojo/Substitute Creature
description: Save Mojo: An animal activist group sets out to protect Mojo, ensuring that he can behave like the naturally evil monkey that he is./Substitute Creature: A substitute teacher comes to Pokey Oaks and the girls are sure that this creature teacher is up to no good.

title: This Is Not a Drill
description: Mega Man and Dr. Light must set aside a father-son disagreement to stop Drill Man from taking revenge on his own overbearing father.

title: El Origen de las Especies Parte 1
description: Dan conoce a su pareja Bakugan, Drago, por primera vez y nos enteramos del "incidente" que ocurrió en la Tierra hace doce años.

title: Tienda De Mascotas
description: En este episodio sobre los primeros años de vida de los Osos, se cuenta la historia del lugar en el que vivieron alguna vez cuando eran bebés. Luego de un altercado con el equipo que filmaba un video absolutamente conmovedor de adopción de animales, los Osos por poco aprovechan la oportunidad de encontrar hogares alejados uno del otro.

title: Trash Boat
description: Rigby changes his name so that he can be cooler.

title: Enemigo Mimo
description: Cuando el departamento del sheriff se enfrenta a un monstruo que copia todos los movimientos, tendrán que encontrar el modo de pelear sin pelear.

title: Powerless
description: The ninja rush to the NINJAGO Museum of History to recover a dangerous scroll before it falls into the hands of the Serpentine Sorceress Aspheera.

title: Big Reveal
description: KO finds out who his father is.

title: Battle for Cybertron III Part 1
description: While the battle rages on the surface, deep below ground Hot Rod faces off against an unexpected traitor, giving Cheetor and Bee time to get the Allspark to the Well.

title: The Responsible
description: Gumball and Darwin babysit Anais "responsibly", whilst "irresponsibly" flooding the house.

title: Outfoxed
description: When Rufus and Reg come to swindle the town, Sheriff Mao Mao teaches them a lesson in justice.

title: Storm in the Room
description: Steven goes into his room in the temple to look for answers.

title: Not Impressed
description: When a Sweetypie isn't impressed with the sheriff dept's antics, our three heroes try everything to win him over.

title: Video Game Wizard
description: Mordecai and Rigby enter a video game tournament to win a video game controller.

title: Jefe por un dia
description: Cuando Chata deja que Vic sea el jefe del puesto de tacos por un día, él decide despedir a Val, lo que trae consecuencias desastrosas.
